Output rollback.gif
Set Theme "Builtin Light"
Set Shell bash
Type "cat /etc/fedora-release"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2
Type "sudo bootc status"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2
Type "fastfetch"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2
Type "cowsay I am Fedora 42 now."
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2
Type "sudo bootc rollback"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 7
